text: Sarah Johnson may refer to: * Sarah Johnson (poet) (born 1980), South African poet * Sarah Anne Johnson (born 1976), Canadian artist * Sarah Johnson (swimmer) (born 1992), Northern Mariana Islands swimmer who participated in Swimming at the 2007 World Aquatics Championships – Women's 400 metre freestyle * Sarah Marie Johnson (born 1987), American teenager convicted in the murder of Diane and Alan Scott Johnson, her parents
title: Sarah Johnson
